This button is inspired by [url=http://custombuttons.sourceforge.net/forum/viewtopic.php?f=6&t=3593]a post/request by [b]JohnPaige[/b][/url]. It allows to switch the value of any preference of any type. This version is similar to [url=http://custombuttons.sourceforge.net/forum/viewtopic.php?f=4&t=3758]Preference Switcher (Basic)[/url], but this one has more features.

